 *
 * group:game_3 => 卡片3配置
 * texts.game_3_badge => 卡片3徽章:text:Classic Pace
 * texts.game_3_title => 卡片3标题:text:Night Table
 * texts.game_3_desc => 卡片3描述:textarea:A darker live roulette lane with stronger focus on the wheel and stake zones.
 * texts.game_3_tag => 卡片3标签:text:Night Table
 * texts.game_3_url => 卡片3链接:text:#download
 *
 * group:game_4 => 卡片4配置
 * texts.game_4_badge => 卡片4徽章:text:Private Lounge
 * texts.game_4_title => 卡片4标题:text:Private Pit
 * texts.game_4_desc => 卡片4描述:textarea:A tighter roulette route for invite groups, returning players, and focused sessions.
 * texts.game_4_tag => 卡片4标签:text:Invite Group
