 * texts.game_5_title => 卡片5标题:text:Streak Room
 * texts.game_5_desc => 卡片5描述:textarea:Built for players who like faster table turns and immediate re-entry.
 * texts.game_5_tag => 卡片5标签:text:Fast Re-entry
 * texts.game_5_url => 卡片5链接:text:#download
 *
 * group:game_6 => 卡片6配置
 * texts.game_6_badge => 卡片6徽章:text:Beginner Friendly
 * texts.game_6_title => 卡片6标题:text:Starter Wheel
 * texts.game_6_desc => 卡片6描述:textarea:A cleaner roulette lane that helps new players settle in before moving faster.
 * texts.game_6_tag => 卡片6标签:text:Easy Start
